twitux (0.69-4) unstable; urgency=low

  * Make removal of /var/lib/scrollkeeper conditional on it having been
    created.
    Thanks Luke Cycon <lcycon@gmail.com> for the diagnosis (Closes: #533956).
  * Import Ben Hearsum's patch to fix the use of wrong avatar pictures.
  * Import as a patch the diff to svn trunk revision 388
     + Add simplied chinese, Korean, Norwegian translations.
     + Update Japanese translation.
     + Resize avatar pictures for display (Closes: #521773).
     + Remove intltool-* from Makefile.am to make it work with newer intltool
  * Remove call to deprecated dh_scrollkeeper.
  * Use quilt to manage patches
  * Updated Standards-Version to 3.8.3. No changes required.

